{"id":1317627530,"question_id":3468,"lang":"rust","lang_name":"Rust","time":"2 weeks, 1 day","timestamp":1720706300,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"0 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1317627530/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Encrypted String","memory":"2.2 MB","code":"\nimpl Solution {\n    pub fn get_encrypted_string(s: String, k: i32) -> String {\n        let n = s.len();\n        let k = (k as usize) % n;  \n        let mut cs = vec![' '; n];\n        let s_chars: Vec<char> = s.chars().collect();\n\n        for i in 0..n {\n            cs[i] = s_chars[(i + k) % n];\n        }\n\n        cs.into_iter().collect()\n    }\n}\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-encrypted-string","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
